description:
Are you looking for high-quality SMA cables?

Buy SMA cables that are ideal for use in commercial and industrial applications. The connector assemblies feature gold-plated Amphenol RF 50 Ω SMA connectors, straight plugs, R/A plugs, straight jacks, and bulkhead jacks. Flexible options include RG-142/U, RG-174/U, RG-316/U double braided, and RG-58/U. Conformable semi-rigid options include both 0.085" and 0.141". Contact us today to learn more!

We have the perfect cable assembly for your needs – contact us today to find out more about our products! You’ll be glad you did when you see how easy it is to buy from us with our fast shipping times and competitive prices on all of our products!
